prcStep.stepDesc:
Added Annexations from Late July 2012 through October 2012.
Lots of old details added by Daisy Tamayo.

Added Annexations from October 2012 through May 2013.
Added Park Annexation to Enumclaw from 1996 which was brought to light only since last update.
Historic details added by Daisy Tamayo including changes to KC boundary along the white river
Updated Woodinville boundary at Woodinville-Duvall road to correct a long standing, recently discovered positional error.
Updated with several annexations of varying vintages. Several ROW annexations now documented.
Updated with several annexations, most notably Bothel Islands.

Updated with 3 effective Renton annexations, 1 pending Issaquah annexation, and a proposed annexation each for Seattle and Sammamish. Many thanks to Daisy Tamayo for her tireless efforts mapping legal descriptions.
